{"tid":1054384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解當朋友拍拖，自己竟然會有複雜嘅心情？！","createTime":"2019-03-09T18:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T00:17:48.000Z","uid":199292,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"010fb618143abac89f2c71382d44d11609ad00e8","tid":1054384,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:48:09.000Z","msg":"當你朋友同你講，佢同人開始咗啦<br />\n<br />\n你會知道，佢冇得再好似以前咁<br />\n你一個電話wts就出嚟陪你吹水出街鳩fing<br />\n唔會再喺你悶嘅時候應你whatsapp<br />\n唔可以再咁易就通頂直落，隨時打牌飲嘢出夜街<br />\n你地嘅話題從始會出現多一個人<br />\n<br />\n但係friend嚟㗎喎，邊可以咁自私咁諗<br />\n唔係應該替佢開心、祝佢地幸福？<br />\n你知道佢有拖拍，係應該開心嘅<br />\n唔會再喺你隔離叫春煩住你<br />\n<br />\n但自己一個人諗嘢嘅時候，一諗返起佢對你宣佈呢個消息嘅語氣<br />\n成個人就會突然down咗落嚟<br />\n<br />\n呢種心情，有冇人明？"},{"pid":"761869b3ab230c18eb81e5f0da23475606a8d87d","tid":1054384,"uid":31290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:48:58.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3bd0930f585876ccfd814da6bf482d4eb51ca7","tid":1054384,"uid":165510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:49:53.000Z","msg":"明白 好似突然間比人搶咗個fd咁<br />\n但其實好鄧佢開心有人照顧佢對佢好<br />\n不過好似有種失落感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d47fb7359b0af0ea39c65c8b1ea8903a2f28d5","tid":1054384,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761869b3ab230c18eb81e5f0da23475606a8d87d","tid":1054384,"uid":31290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:48:58.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:50:05.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7fa7c3087b7788eb68e919827328be0847cc09","tid":1054384,"uid":31290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1d47fb7359b0af0ea39c65c8b1ea8903a2f28d5","tid":1054384,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761869b3ab230c18eb81e5f0da23475606a8d87d","tid":